      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> halved potatoes</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for an initial 10 min or until slightly tender</p>",
