      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes cook, add your<strong> egg[s]</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for exactly 8 min for a perfect, mid-boiled egg</p><p>Once done, drain and refill the pot with <strong>ice-cold water</strong> and the<strong> cooked egg[s]</strong>, then set them aside to cool</p>",
