    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and grate your<strong> garlic </strong>and cut your <strong>lime[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper, remove the <strong>outer</strong> <strong>leaves </strong>and set aside, shred the<strong> inner core[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber </strong>in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p>",
